{"tid":2386572,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"請問如何召煥惡魔？","createTime":"2021-01-29T16:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T07:24:04.000Z","uid":139103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2fb0555caf2b1d056a5e58fd34f8c14c3b29b9","tid":2386572,"uid":139103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"惡魔高校啲女好正，我都想召煥。"},{"pid":"45124f380f53d28476a60c8e993c47001c9b7d9f","tid":2386572,"uid":374353,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"學拉丁文<br />\n啲文法讀錯哂佢就會好似連登仔咁出嚟屌柒你"},{"pid":"c4b047420ee6eca5d363b7631973ec9580af9128","tid":2386572,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4200858fad2813cbd3d93ffba6217d0172a967","tid":2386572,"uid":139103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45124f380f53d28476a60c8e993c47001c9b7d9f","tid":2386572,"uid":374353,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"學拉丁文<br />\n啲文法讀錯哂佢就會好似連登仔咁出嚟屌柒你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"YouTube 有冇片可以跟住讀？"},{"pid":"51b1378a08eef9566fbb09d51cfdf789b3b87d30","tid":2386572,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T11:57:48.000Z","msg":"唔關方法事<br />\n唔係被選嘅人召唔到"},{"pid":"687148b58900a95d7736c5dfe1685d2ad04ed74a","tid":2386572,"uid":373794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb2fb0555caf2b1d056a5e58fd34f8c14c3b29b9","tid":2386572,"uid":139103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"惡魔高校啲女好正，我都想召煥。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:24:04.000Z","msg":"惡魔個樣好醜怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你召喚成功之後，唔好後悔，同埋一樣野：召喚等同敵對上帝，你仲敢唔敢？<br />\n<br />\nok, whatever la,方法如下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evocation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FEvocation&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=016c5c7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evocation</a><br />\n召喚惡魔/惡靈/魔鬼撒旦etc嘅原理係邪念，只要你離開正道，魔鬼就好容易入侵你嘅思想同身體，最後佢會引導你入地獄。<br />\n魔鬼其實一直都工作緊，凡是惡嘅形象都係嚟自佢，但係魔鬼同天使都係人死後而變，所以人類係先於靈嘅存在。基本上，你唔需要刻意/努力行惡，你只要跟隨本性就可以離開正道。<br />\n<br />\n歷史上，都有唔少人都召喚惡魔，成功可以叫佢地幫手做d野，自己google下就搵到<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%AD%94%E9%AC%BC%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25AD%2594%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=05b920c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%AD%94%E9%AC%BC%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93</a><br />\n我唔認為方法最重要，你向魔嘅心先係最重要，只要你好努力地求惡魔幫你，佢就會出現。<br />\n問題係你究竟可以畀到d咩代價令佢幫你？每個人求嘅野都唔同，所以代價都唔同，呢一層你要同佢傾點數，所以答唔到你。"}]}